 gẖyrh yqdr ygẖfr ạldẖnwb
 wḥdh ạlly yqdr ygẖfr ạldẖnwb ạ̹lh ạlạ̉ḥbạb kẖạlq
 ạlạ̉kwạn
 ạlqrạr- kẖạṭy kẖạṭy kẖạṭy wbạtwb myn gẖyrh yqdr
 ygẖfr ạldẖnwb
